title: OnePlus 9 Astral Black, 5G Unlocked Android Smartphone U.S Version, 8GB RAM+128GB Storage,120Hz Fluid Display (Renewed)
description: PRODUCT OVERVIEWThe new OnePlus 9 is finally here, offering premium flagship features at an affordable price. The device features a Hasselblad triple camera system for vivid and natural-looking pictures. Get a full day’s power with only half an hour plugged in thanks to Warp Charge 65T. With 5G and an immersive 120Hz Fluid Display, you're all set to take your gaming to the next level. The OnePlus 9 includes Alexa and Google Assistant Built-in, providing hands-free experience.KEY FEATURESHasselblad Camera for Mobile - Take your best shot with the OnePlus 9 5G Triple Camera system co-developed with Hasselblad.Broaden every horizon with one of the largest Ultra-Wide sensor - The 50 MP Ultra-Wide Camera offers unparalleled clarity with its pioneering Freeform Lens.Capture breathtaking 8K - With 8K video, your favorite memories live forever in sensational detail.Fast and Smooth Performance - The Qualcomm Snapdragon 888 with 5G delivers unprecedented power with every aspect of performance boosted 25% over Snapdragon 865.A Day’s Power in 15 Minutes - With Warp Charge 65T and a large 4500mAh battery, get a day's power in 15 minutes of charging, and getting to that complete 100% charge only takes 29 minutes.120Hz Fluid Display - The 6.55" FHD+ AMOLED display offers ultra-smooth 120Hz scrolling to deliver a flagship visual experience.Designed by OnePlus - OnePlus 9 5G blends creativity and premium materials into a single unibody experience.128 GB Storage CapacityStore hundreds of songs, films, games, and more with 128GB of storage capacity available on your OnePlus 9.5G Capable - Experience faster upload and download speeds along with lower latency when connected to a 5G network (only compatible with T-Mobile 5G)Alexa and Google Assistant Support - OnePlus 9 5G includes Alexa and Google Assistant Built-in, providing hands-free experience.
